SwiftUI MVVM App

- Folders for every part of the UI
- @State boolean variables and toggle() based on button press -> .fullScreenCover (partial full screen new view)
- NavigationStack, NavigationLink (for non-value based navigation), ScrollView + toolbar, VStack, HStack, Image, Text, TextField + SecureField for user input, List
- @Environment(\.dismiss) var dismiss
- Custom divider line like Divider() using Rectangle()
- Styling
- List is scrollable by default